深化移风易俗工作导则》等文件要求，加大移风易俗宣传活动，健全完善长效机制，充分发挥「红白理事会」作用，加强典型示范引领，用身边榜样教育影响村民，带动民风，树立文明新风尚。 同在 6 月 27 日，共青团宁南县委发出的一份倡议书提到：广大青年要厉行勤俭节约，鼓励带头不举办、不参加小孩满月、周岁、庆生、升学、入伍、购车、乔迁、履新、开业庆典、就业等各类收礼性宴请。严格遵守村规民约和居民公约，文明操办婚丧嫁娶事宜，自觉抵制他有我有互攀比、奢华阔气显排场的不良习气。严格遵守红白喜事执行标准，注重餐食安全干净卫生，自觉养成文明就餐习惯，自觉抵制蹲地用餐、塑料盆装肉盛汤等不良习俗。四川凉山治理「蹲地用餐」等，官方倡议青年自觉抵制 _ 文明 _ 工作时 _ 彩礼"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d360e702377c80cea675cb1b13d22e29_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/541411259"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqODW8a3G+r1PEAMaCDgyNTk1NTEzIOuniZYGMCs4xwRAI3IJNTQxNDExMjU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1656982212.4491506", "card_id": "Q_537662683", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 447}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "未婚夫用合成钻石跟你求婚，你会答应吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a17cad97c2457437d18c1dfeb0e97d64_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/537662683"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqODW8a3G+r1PEAMaCDgxNzYyNTI4IPzroJUGMDU4rQRAJHIJNTM3NjYyNjgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1656982212.4496784", "card_id": "Q_541171913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《中国说唱巅峰对决》艾热为什么会输给热狗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3aa29fd41bd313d48e8c9dcd0755332c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link